OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ffirst with a scattering of showers.
OL,7,FClear spells developing across Cumbria
OL,8,Fthis evening and then more widely
OL,9,Flater in the night. Becoming cold with
OL,10,Fa fairly widespread frost in the
OL,11,Fcountryside.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAfter a largely dry start
OL,14,Fwith sunny periods, cloud will bubble
OL,15,Fup to give a somewhat cloudier
OL,16,Fafternoon. An isolated shower is
OL,17,Fpossible but most places staying dry.
OL,18,FFeeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
