OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FAfter
OL,6,Fchilly starts, Thursday and Friday
OL,7,Fwill be dry for many, but showers are
OL,8,Fpossible, these locally heavy on
OL,9,FFriday. Longer periods of rain are
OL,10,Fpossible on Saturday. Turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
